casebody.data:
Hanscel, Appellant, et al. v. Watters et al., Appellees.

[Cite as Hanscel v. Watters (1986), 28 Ohio St. 3d 136.]

No. 86-592 Decided December 24, 1986. Matan & Smith, Eugene L. Matan and James D. Coiner, for appellant. Bricker & Eckler, Richard T. Taps and Martha Post Baxter, for ap-pellees.

The judgment of the court of appeals in case No. 85AP-743 is hereby affirmed on authority of Evans v. Chapman (1986), 28 Ohio St. 3d 132, decided this day.

Celebrezze, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, C. Brown, Douglas and Wright, JJ., concur.
